TITLE: Implementing Pagination with Knp Paginator in Pimcore
DESCRIPTION: Complete example of implementing pagination using Knp Paginator, including controller action, view template, and pagination partial.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pimcore/pimcore/blob/12.x/doc/05_Objects/03_Working_with_PHP_API.md#2025-04-17_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
public function testAction(Request $request, \Knp\Component\Pager\PaginatorInterface $paginator): Response
{
    $list = new DataObject\Simple\Listing();
    $list->setOrderKey("name");
    $list->setOrder("asc");

    $paginator = $paginator->paginate(
        $list,
        $request->query->getInt('page', 1),
        10
    );

    return $this->render('Test/Test.html.twig', [
        'paginator' => $paginator,
        'paginationVariables' => $paginator->getPaginationData()
    ]);
```

LANGUAGE: twig
CODE:
```
{% for item in paginator %}
    <h2>{{ item.name }}</h2>
{% endfor %}
<br />

{% include 'includes/pagination.html.twig' %}
