SOURCE: https://github.com/pimcore/pimcore/blob/12.x/doc/20_Extending_Pimcore/13_Bundle_Developers_Guide/13_Loading_Admin_UI_Assets.md#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: php
