TITLE: Implementing Editable Dialog Box for Areabrick in PHP
DESCRIPTION: Example of implementing the EditableDialogBoxInterface to provide additional configuration options for an area brick. This class creates a dialog with input, checkbox, and date fields.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pimcore/pimcore/blob/12.x/doc/03_Documents/01_Editables/02_Areablock/02_Bricks.md#2025-04-17_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: php
