TITLE: Media Query Handling in PHP
DESCRIPTION: Examples of handling media queries in thumbnail configurations and generating responsive images.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pimcore/pimcore/blob/12.x/doc/04_Assets/03_Working_with_Thumbnails/01_Image_Thumbnails.md#2025-04-17_snippet_10

